Draw a class Diagram with class relations
In Hospital management system users can login as doctor and patient and provide authentication to
users. Patient can book appointment. There are several departments in hospital like ENT, Cardiac,
Orthopedic, neurology and so on. Hospital is providing services of medicine and surgery. Patient can
view their profile as detail, make payment, take drugs and receive their reports. Doctor can check
patient, suggest drugs, view repots and manage their other responsibilities. Staff assist patient and
doctors, also get payment from patient and provide drug to patient. Administrator manage doctor and
Staff records using crud operations manage their timetable and salaries. This system will store record
of all users, administrator and drugs that staff gives to patients.
